WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:07.916
A NETFLIX SERIES

00:24.666 --> 00:26.625
WHEN ARE WE HAVING DINNER?

00:37.958 --> 00:40.000
Are you with us, Doni?

00:40.083 --> 00:42.708
Yeah. Sounds great. Whose song is that?

00:42.791 --> 00:46.000
It could be yours.
It's called "Who Can Take It?"

00:46.083 --> 00:48.875
I'm trying a collab with you
and Theo Ribeiro.

00:48.958 --> 00:50.041
What do you think?

00:51.041 --> 00:53.083
But Theo Ribeiro is an influencer.

00:53.166 --> 00:54.708
He does everything.

00:54.791 --> 00:56.250
What about Kevinho?

00:56.333 --> 00:58.166
Everything in its own time.

00:58.666 --> 01:00.583
Marcão, isn't the song great?

01:00.666 --> 01:02.000
Great. It's a hit.

01:04.708 --> 01:06.250
Check this out.

01:06.750 --> 01:08.666
Great marketing.

01:08.750 --> 01:11.666
Damn. He's a poster boy for many brands.

01:11.750 --> 01:13.541
You can get a sponsor too.

01:13.625 --> 01:16.375
He's one of the greatest
Tik-Tokers in Brazil.

01:16.458 --> 01:18.833
A collab with him will be a hit.

01:18.916 --> 01:20.458
Everyone wins.

01:20.541 --> 01:22.791
This one will top the charts.

01:26.625 --> 01:29.250
I have a song. It's almost ready.

01:29.333 --> 01:33.041
Doni, you're very talented.
But it's a partnership,

01:33.125 --> 01:34.500
not a competition.

01:34.583 --> 01:36.875
You don't need to fight each other.

01:36.958 --> 01:39.041
It's to showcase both of you.

01:39.125 --> 01:40.875
I know, but it's almost done.

01:41.791 --> 01:43.125
I'll bring it this week.

01:46.583 --> 01:48.750
Alright. I trust you.

01:49.500 --> 01:50.333
Deal.

01:55.291 --> 01:57.875
I'm fucked, man. I've got no song.

01:57.958 --> 02:00.875
You're unbelievable. Fuck.

02:06.083 --> 02:07.833
BASED ON THE ORIGINAL IDEA
BY KONDZILLA

02:07.916 --> 02:11.208
It'll be very roomy.
One row here, another one there.

02:11.291 --> 02:13.541
It'll be great, Pastor.

02:14.041 --> 02:16.041
I can see the church already.

02:16.750 --> 02:18.625
All the blessings.

02:19.333 --> 02:21.375
All the anointing, Pastor.

02:21.833 --> 02:23.500
Beautiful! Thank God!

02:23.583 --> 02:25.791
I'm seeing things I didn't before.

02:25.875 --> 02:27.291
Water damage, Rita!

02:27.375 --> 02:29.958
Pastor, problems can be fixed.

02:30.041 --> 02:33.208
Look at this church.
It's important to the community.

02:33.708 --> 02:35.208
I'd be lost without it.

02:35.291 --> 02:37.208
I hope we don't take five years

02:37.291 --> 02:39.083
to finish the remodel.

02:39.166 --> 02:43.166
Pastor, don't forget
you're talking to a true grinder.

02:43.250 --> 02:44.666
Doing God's work.

02:45.208 --> 02:48.875
I got approval from the city
and the head pastors.

02:48.958 --> 02:51.791
Now, the hardest part. Donations.

02:58.708 --> 02:59.958
Hey, brother.

03:00.041 --> 03:01.333
All cool?

03:01.416 --> 03:04.583
-What's with the bike?
-It's hard work.

03:04.666 --> 03:07.333
-He's here.
-The boss has arrived.

03:11.250 --> 03:12.708
How's it going, man?

03:12.791 --> 03:14.250
-You cool?
-What's up?

03:14.333 --> 03:16.375
-All good?
-Great.

03:16.458 --> 03:18.000
-Hey.
-What's up?

03:18.083 --> 03:20.833
Man, we sold almost half of the load.

03:20.916 --> 03:23.750
-It's going great.
-It's flowing, man.

03:23.833 --> 03:25.708
The mix is really working!

03:25.791 --> 03:29.208
We're very busy.
I think I'm hiring another person.

03:29.291 --> 03:30.166
Great, man.

03:30.250 --> 03:32.375
-You're the manager now.
-You got it.

03:32.458 --> 03:34.583
Bro, I did the math.

03:34.666 --> 03:36.791
If we buy and mix more,

03:36.875 --> 03:38.416
the profits will double.

03:38.500 --> 03:40.250
-Great, man.
-We'll be cool.

03:42.041 --> 03:44.166
I don't know if I can get it.

03:44.875 --> 03:46.916
Help us out, man.

03:47.000 --> 03:48.250
-We need you.
-Trust us.

03:48.750 --> 03:52.750
I will try to get a discount
with half upfront

03:53.250 --> 03:54.708
and pay the rest later.

03:55.416 --> 03:58.125
If we do that, can we pay in three months?

03:58.208 --> 04:00.916
So, based on my numbers…

04:03.916 --> 04:04.750
That's right.

04:04.833 --> 04:08.083
We'll pay it off in three months
with extra to spare.

04:08.166 --> 04:10.708
Trust me. It'll work.

04:13.875 --> 04:15.375
Good fucking recruiting, man.

04:15.458 --> 04:17.000
-He's a beast, huh?
-Awesome.

04:17.083 --> 04:19.250
I'll talk to Messinho.

04:19.333 --> 04:20.250
You got a deal.

04:20.333 --> 04:22.166
-Cool.
-Help us out.

04:22.250 --> 04:23.083
Alright.

04:23.166 --> 04:26.458
Gotta get the numbers right, man.

04:31.708 --> 04:35.458
She loves me and tries to control me

04:35.541 --> 04:38.458
Rivaldo, it's golden.

04:39.291 --> 04:41.583
I'm getting emotional.

04:41.666 --> 04:43.958
What are the boys going to do?

04:44.458 --> 04:48.375
Everyone from all sides
want to get a haircut from us.

04:48.458 --> 04:51.416
Shit is going to get real.

04:51.500 --> 04:55.375
What a crazy girl
Keeps trying to control me

04:55.458 --> 04:57.291
Then she walks away

04:57.375 --> 04:59.375
She walks away

04:59.458 --> 05:01.666
It's imported, man.

05:02.583 --> 05:06.458
This girl is annoying
She's always complaining

05:06.541 --> 05:08.458
Then she walks away

05:08.541 --> 05:10.583
She walks away

05:10.666 --> 05:12.458
Am I on the right path?

05:13.291 --> 05:15.916
Yeah, you totally are.

05:19.958 --> 05:21.666
And what about Theo?

05:22.958 --> 05:24.666
What? Theo Ribeiro?

05:25.333 --> 05:28.083
-You know him?
-He's got pictures with Neymar.

05:28.166 --> 05:30.625
Theozinho? No way!

05:30.708 --> 05:34.833
Man, the guy's a great fucking singer.

05:34.916 --> 05:36.625
And he's got presence.

05:36.708 --> 05:37.875
Show him.

05:40.291 --> 05:41.875
The guy's cool.

05:41.958 --> 05:45.250
I know a guy who works for him,
says he's cool.

05:45.333 --> 05:46.750
Very generous.

05:46.833 --> 05:50.791
But he's not a musician.
He's a TikToker. Get it?

05:52.958 --> 05:55.125
We could send him some clothes.

05:56.291 --> 05:57.541
What, man?

05:57.625 --> 06:00.041
Stop kissing his butt and let me write.

06:04.041 --> 06:05.875
Then she walks away

06:07.166 --> 06:08.833
No, wait.

06:08.916 --> 06:11.416
It's better if we turn it around.

06:11.500 --> 06:12.791
To get everything.

06:13.291 --> 06:14.541
Wow.

06:15.416 --> 06:17.791
You're a jack-of-all-trades, Rita.

06:19.083 --> 06:19.958
It's great.

06:20.666 --> 06:22.625
It's so great to see this moving along.

06:23.666 --> 06:24.500
Yeah.

06:25.708 --> 06:28.083
And speaking of which,

06:29.041 --> 06:33.041
you really think your father
wouldn't help the church?

06:35.458 --> 06:36.458
I don't know, Rita.

06:36.958 --> 06:40.083
I know my father.
I can imagine what he'll say.

06:40.583 --> 06:43.125
"Honey, I know it's for a noble cause,

06:43.208 --> 06:45.958
but we're already paying
the church's rent."

06:46.541 --> 06:50.125
"Do you know how many congregations
can't pay their bills?"

06:52.041 --> 06:53.583
What if I talk to him?

06:54.333 --> 06:55.333
Levi?

06:55.875 --> 06:57.208
Come down here, please.

06:58.375 --> 07:01.875
-You okay?
-We need more food. There's a lot to do.

07:01.958 --> 07:03.750
The donor owns the market.

07:03.833 --> 07:06.333
He told me we could call him.

07:06.416 --> 07:07.833
-I got it.
-Thanks.

07:08.416 --> 07:11.916
Levi, what if I contacted
the large donors directly

07:12.000 --> 07:13.916
about remodeling the church?

07:15.833 --> 07:17.291
God's really using you.

07:31.791 --> 07:32.750
Thanks, bud.

07:43.291 --> 07:46.416
Hey, Nando. All good?
I need to talk to you.

07:48.000 --> 07:49.416
All's good with me.

07:49.500 --> 07:50.875
Tell me what you need.

07:51.916 --> 07:55.416
It's about a song. I need your help.

07:55.500 --> 07:57.333
Do you have time now?

07:58.166 --> 08:02.000
I'm a bit busy, man. But sing it to me.

08:03.666 --> 08:05.666
Alright, I only got the chorus.

08:05.750 --> 08:09.458
She says she trusts me
But always with suspicion

08:09.541 --> 08:11.291
Then she walks away

08:11.375 --> 08:13.416
Then she walks away

08:13.500 --> 08:17.125
Possessive woman
She's always complaining

08:17.208 --> 08:18.791
Then she walks away

08:18.875 --> 08:20.875
Then she walks away

08:20.958 --> 08:22.458
What do you think?

08:22.541 --> 08:25.708
To be honest,
the melody is great, but the lyrics…

08:25.791 --> 08:28.041
It's not you, man. For real.

08:28.541 --> 08:31.166
I'm fucked. I need to submit something.

08:31.250 --> 08:33.125
I want them to believe in me.

08:33.833 --> 08:37.208
Bro, everyone believes in your potential.

08:37.291 --> 08:40.750
Do your own thing. It'll be fine.

08:40.833 --> 08:42.083
I'm kind of busy,

08:42.166 --> 08:44.375
but I'll call you when I'm done.

08:44.875 --> 08:46.125
Later, man.

08:58.708 --> 09:00.708
-Sup, Nando.
-Sup, bro.

09:00.791 --> 09:02.875
-All good?
-Good.

09:02.958 --> 09:05.291
How's the shop and the family?

09:05.375 --> 09:08.333
-All good, brother.
-What do you need?

09:08.916 --> 09:10.666
I have a proposal for you.

09:11.166 --> 09:14.416
Your product is great.
It sold like hot cakes.

09:14.916 --> 09:17.500
-I was crunching the numbers--
-Relax, man.

09:17.583 --> 09:19.875
Let me order a drink. Hey.

09:21.291 --> 09:23.416
Gin and tonic, please.

09:30.416 --> 09:32.500
What does Badá want now?

09:32.583 --> 09:34.166
He didn't send me today.

09:34.250 --> 09:35.458
I came on my own.

09:36.083 --> 09:37.833
That shop is mine now.

09:40.833 --> 09:42.000
Shoot.

09:42.083 --> 09:43.541
Business is great.

09:43.625 --> 09:45.666
We'll double the revenue soon.

09:46.208 --> 09:49.333
I want twice as much this time.

09:49.416 --> 09:52.041
I'll pay half now and the rest in a month.

09:53.416 --> 09:54.416
Deal?

09:58.000 --> 09:59.750
Let me ask you something.

10:00.916 --> 10:02.333
How big is your business?

10:02.875 --> 10:03.916
Just the shop.

10:07.250 --> 10:09.416
I'll give you some advice.

10:10.041 --> 10:11.416
Free of charge.

10:12.375 --> 10:13.875
Diversify it.

10:14.500 --> 10:15.458
Understand?

10:15.958 --> 10:17.125
Open a…

10:17.833 --> 10:19.625
restaurant,

10:20.166 --> 10:21.708
a nightclub.

10:22.375 --> 10:25.458
Open a gas station, a car wash,

10:25.541 --> 10:27.250
a hotel, something like that.

10:28.416 --> 10:30.458
How much does a gin and tonic cost?

10:31.375 --> 10:33.875
The gin, the tonic, the bartender…

10:34.708 --> 10:37.166
How much for the entertainment,

10:37.250 --> 10:38.416
the singers?

10:42.166 --> 10:43.833
As much as I want.

10:45.625 --> 10:48.625
It costs what the owner decides.

10:49.125 --> 10:50.458
I understand, bro.

10:50.541 --> 10:52.875
Like hotel tariffs and things like that.

10:52.958 --> 10:54.208
Exactly.

10:55.041 --> 10:56.500
You gotta diversify.

10:58.291 --> 11:00.666
But I was thinking and it's legit.

11:01.458 --> 11:03.583
If you give me some time to pay,

11:03.666 --> 11:05.500
you'll get the money, trust me.

11:08.125 --> 11:11.375
I made an exception for Badá.

11:12.166 --> 11:14.416
I can't do that for everyone.

11:15.625 --> 11:16.458
It's business.

11:19.708 --> 11:21.458
Think about what I said.

11:21.541 --> 11:23.708
Don't settle for just one little shop.

11:26.375 --> 11:27.458
But I'll help you.

11:28.166 --> 11:30.333
What I can do with the load

11:31.208 --> 11:34.500
is half upfront, half when you pay it off.

11:35.583 --> 11:36.625
Alright?

11:41.416 --> 11:42.708
Thanks, bro.

11:45.208 --> 11:46.583
I appreciate your trust.

11:51.458 --> 11:55.375
What a crazy girl
Keeps trying to control me

11:55.458 --> 11:57.375
Then she walks away

11:59.583 --> 12:01.833
-What?
-It's horrible.

12:01.916 --> 12:02.833
What's wrong?

12:04.750 --> 12:05.666
Nothing.

12:07.291 --> 12:11.000
This girl is annoying
She's always complaining

12:11.083 --> 12:13.125
Then she walks away

12:13.208 --> 12:14.958
She walks away…

12:22.750 --> 12:23.916
Hey, guys.

12:24.583 --> 12:26.791
I'm sorry if I was rude.

12:26.875 --> 12:28.083
I was tense.

12:29.250 --> 12:31.666
Do you want to tell me something?

12:33.083 --> 12:34.541
We have a cousin.

12:35.458 --> 12:36.875
That again?

12:36.958 --> 12:38.833
Yeah, man.

12:38.916 --> 12:40.666
A very cool cousin.

12:41.166 --> 12:44.750
We've been meaning to show you her music.

12:44.833 --> 12:47.125
I think that it's time, you know?

12:47.208 --> 12:48.916
But she's a bit touchy.

12:49.000 --> 12:51.000
She's insolent, Jaspion.

12:51.583 --> 12:52.500
Bold.

12:53.666 --> 12:56.833
The girl likes attention
and you want her here?

12:56.916 --> 12:59.083
I didn't say that. Her name's Luzia.

12:59.166 --> 13:02.000
-MC Luzi now.
-She's cool.

13:02.916 --> 13:05.500
Can I hear her music?

13:05.583 --> 13:08.041
Sure, of course. Here.

13:12.291 --> 13:13.458
Hear this.

13:13.541 --> 13:15.541
It's finally Friday

13:15.625 --> 13:18.916
I'm all ready to go out

13:19.000 --> 13:20.000
It's cool!

13:20.083 --> 13:22.291
Saying stupid things

13:22.375 --> 13:24.666
Thinking you're the boss of me

13:25.708 --> 13:27.833
-Awesome.
-She wrote it.

13:27.916 --> 13:29.916
The beat's hers too.

13:33.666 --> 13:35.041
Hey, Luzi. It's Doni.

13:35.125 --> 13:37.458
Come over. Let's talk.

13:40.500 --> 13:42.083
You're crazy, man.

14:00.375 --> 14:02.250
-Hey, sister.
-Hey.

14:02.916 --> 14:03.833
How are you?

14:05.708 --> 14:08.041
Let's visit Mr. Leonel.

14:08.125 --> 14:10.125
He sells gutters in Santana.

14:10.208 --> 14:12.083
My gut tells me he'll help.

14:12.166 --> 14:14.583
Levi with his jokes.

14:15.375 --> 14:16.208
Sorry.

14:16.291 --> 14:17.416
Alright, let's go.

14:17.500 --> 14:18.541
-Let's.
-Yep.

14:18.625 --> 14:20.666
When are we having another cheeseburger?

14:20.750 --> 14:22.708
-You really liked it.
-I did.

14:23.208 --> 14:24.708
I was thinking,

14:24.791 --> 14:27.333
I need more gospel playlists.

14:27.416 --> 14:30.375
-Maybe rap, international songs.
-I have many.

14:30.458 --> 14:32.541
Really? Can you share them?

14:32.625 --> 14:35.458
-Awesome.
-We don't play them during service.

14:36.250 --> 14:39.166
I forgot. Eliseu and Raquel
are coming too.

14:39.250 --> 14:40.250
Okay.

14:41.458 --> 14:43.583
Hello, Eliseu. Hey, Raquel.

14:43.666 --> 14:46.875
We're here to watch today.
You are the leaders.

14:46.958 --> 14:49.083
My God, that's a big responsibility.

14:49.166 --> 14:51.041
And we have high expectations.

14:51.125 --> 14:52.958
-Shall we go?
-Let's.

15:08.041 --> 15:10.708
-The boy's flying.
-Man, he even bought an X5.

15:10.791 --> 15:12.916
Really? Fuck.

15:13.000 --> 15:14.000
He's flying.

15:15.791 --> 15:16.625
Open that.

15:17.208 --> 15:18.083
This?

15:21.000 --> 15:23.083
-What's this?
-A gift, fucker.

15:24.500 --> 15:26.666
-No way, man.
-Yeah, it's for you.

15:36.750 --> 15:39.541
-You didn't have to.
-You'll have your own shop.

15:40.708 --> 15:41.875
We're climbing.

15:43.083 --> 15:45.125
This is just the beginning.

15:48.333 --> 15:49.166
Like it?

15:50.333 --> 15:52.708
-Thanks, bro.
-I got your back, man.

16:03.916 --> 16:05.916
-You're losing it.
-You suck, man.

16:06.416 --> 16:08.375
-Another one?
-Forget it, Rivaldo.

16:10.166 --> 16:12.375
-Make the turn.
-Stop it, man.

16:14.583 --> 16:16.583
-She's here.
-Yeah, she's here.

16:20.750 --> 16:22.500
Sup, guys?

16:25.041 --> 16:26.708
-Missed you, bro.
-Cousin!

16:26.791 --> 16:28.500
Word. Excuse me.

16:28.583 --> 16:29.416
Hey.

16:30.083 --> 16:31.333
Hey, man.

16:31.416 --> 16:34.791
I was so glad you called me.
I'm a huge fan.

16:34.875 --> 16:36.708
-Cool.
-Thanks.

16:36.791 --> 16:39.625
-Won't you talk to me?
-I didn't want to.

16:39.708 --> 16:43.250
Cool? Fuck, do it right.

16:43.333 --> 16:44.458
All good?

16:44.541 --> 16:45.375
Fuck!

16:47.708 --> 16:51.166
You really made it, man.
Your place is awesome.

16:51.250 --> 16:52.666
It's huge.

16:52.750 --> 16:54.958
-Do you like it?
-What? Amazing!

16:55.041 --> 16:57.750
I heard your songs. Your stuff's great.

16:57.833 --> 17:00.375
I knew you'd like them.
I have many others.

17:00.458 --> 17:02.166
I'm always writing.

17:02.250 --> 17:04.750
Me too, but the game changes.

17:04.833 --> 17:06.541
I need new partnerships.

17:06.625 --> 17:09.333
So I thought about you.

17:10.125 --> 17:12.500
Awesome. Thanks, man.

17:12.583 --> 17:13.750
It's on.

17:13.833 --> 17:15.416
But, brother…

17:16.166 --> 17:18.875
Listen, brother,

17:19.375 --> 17:20.583
it's hard to get here.

17:21.166 --> 17:24.125
I took a bus, a train, and had to walk.

17:24.208 --> 17:25.541
-It's far.
-No worries.

17:25.625 --> 17:27.583
Do you have anything to drink?

17:28.291 --> 17:30.250
-Sure.
-Just to cool down.

17:30.333 --> 17:32.416
-Wet my whistle.
-I got water, soda…

17:33.375 --> 17:35.333
A shot of the green one?

17:38.208 --> 17:39.041
Alright.

17:39.125 --> 17:40.875
-Coconut water ice?
-Yep.

17:40.958 --> 17:43.833
Alright, excuse me. I'll get it.

17:50.458 --> 17:53.625
What about your contact
who'd discover the rats?

17:54.250 --> 17:57.125
Do you know who ratted us out?

17:57.208 --> 17:58.125
No, man.

17:58.208 --> 18:01.541
Don't worry. When I get him,
I'll crush him myself.

18:01.625 --> 18:04.916
Man, I already told you.
You can't mess up.

18:05.458 --> 18:08.333
When you get him, fuck him up.

18:08.416 --> 18:10.625
-Yeah, man. No talk.
-That's right.

18:10.708 --> 18:12.500
I hope so.

18:12.583 --> 18:15.666
Bro, I wanted to talk to you.

18:15.750 --> 18:18.583
-What's up?
-Talk to Messinho.

18:18.666 --> 18:21.958
I made him a proposal,
but he was suspicious.

18:22.041 --> 18:24.708
Man, Messinho is complicated.

18:25.333 --> 18:27.208
He's always suspicious.

18:27.291 --> 18:30.791
He's always on the lookout,
never lets his guard down.

18:30.875 --> 18:32.958
-I'm good for it.
-I know, man.

18:33.041 --> 18:36.875
You see him just hanging out.
He seems to be chill.

18:36.958 --> 18:39.000
But in reality, he don't play.

18:39.500 --> 18:41.791
Understand, bro? He don't play.

18:42.416 --> 18:43.250
Right.

18:43.750 --> 18:45.125
I owe you one.

