38:32.041 --> 38:33.208
Open your eyes.

38:35.250 --> 38:36.833
Holy Father!

38:38.041 --> 38:39.416
What a blessing, Rita!

38:39.916 --> 38:42.833
Blessed be thy name, Jesus!

38:42.916 --> 38:46.041
-Thank you, Lord. Thanks, honey.
-My pleasure, Pastor.

38:47.750 --> 38:49.875
We won't take five years.

38:49.958 --> 38:52.041
-Of course not!
-No way.

38:52.125 --> 38:54.833
Soon, we'll be praying in a new temple.

38:54.916 --> 38:56.583
Amen, Pastor.

39:02.708 --> 39:04.416
STAFF

39:05.208 --> 39:07.000
-Hey, Marcão!
-Hey, man.

39:07.083 --> 39:09.125
Did you get the green apples?

39:09.750 --> 39:11.375
Man, I forgot.

39:11.875 --> 39:13.791
Green apples, Marcão.

39:13.875 --> 39:16.000
Can't forget the green apples.

39:16.625 --> 39:19.083
Marcão, you screwed up.

39:19.166 --> 39:20.875
Red apples are unacceptable.

39:20.958 --> 39:23.291
He needs green apples for his throat.

39:23.375 --> 39:26.583
I've got a cousin who's a producer.
He needs a job.

39:28.916 --> 39:31.708
Fuck, I never know
when you're screwing with me.

39:34.875 --> 39:36.583
They'll always do that.

39:36.666 --> 39:37.875
Fuck you.

39:41.583 --> 39:44.791
Hey, Marcão. Did you get upset?
It was a joke, man.

39:44.875 --> 39:47.125
What? It's cool, man.

39:50.791 --> 39:52.166
Tally is coming--

39:53.791 --> 39:55.458
What's up, guys?

39:55.541 --> 39:57.041
-Hey.
-Hey.

39:57.125 --> 39:59.125
-Hey, Doni!
-How's it going?

39:59.208 --> 40:00.125
Great.

40:00.208 --> 40:02.166
Fixing the look for TV?

40:02.250 --> 40:03.708
I heard you were coming.

40:04.416 --> 40:06.208
Such bullshit.

40:06.916 --> 40:07.916
I love it.

40:08.666 --> 40:10.458
Came to do a live with me?

40:10.541 --> 40:12.916
I'll be the influencer attraction.

40:13.000 --> 40:15.458
I'll interview Theo Ribeiro.

40:16.708 --> 40:18.916
Really? That's cool.

40:19.500 --> 40:21.291
I gotta go.

40:22.375 --> 40:23.375
Alright.

40:25.250 --> 40:28.083
-Later. Call me.
-Okay.

40:29.416 --> 40:32.541
Doni, I look so good,
they didn't do my makeup.

40:33.208 --> 40:34.250
They didn't?

40:45.041 --> 40:46.541
Marcão, what's going on?

40:48.583 --> 40:50.375
Luzi can't perform.

40:50.458 --> 40:52.500
-What do you mean?
-She can't.

40:52.583 --> 40:54.291
Luan only booked you.

40:54.375 --> 40:55.666
It's her song too.

40:55.750 --> 40:57.833
Yeah, but she's not with Bang Loko.

40:57.916 --> 40:58.791
But she can be.

40:59.291 --> 41:00.583
Man, Luan tried.

41:00.666 --> 41:02.291
He talked to her manager,

41:02.375 --> 41:04.208
he tried to level with him,

41:04.291 --> 41:05.458
but he refused.

41:07.125 --> 41:09.458
That's what her manager wants,
but what about what she wants?

41:09.541 --> 41:11.416
This always happens.

41:11.500 --> 41:15.041
He thinks the money from the song
will make him rich.

41:15.541 --> 41:16.791
What an idiot.

41:17.541 --> 41:19.333
She'll perform. Fuck it.

41:19.416 --> 41:20.541
Calm down, man.

41:20.625 --> 41:22.750
This fight is not worth having.

41:23.500 --> 41:25.583
Business comes before the show.

41:26.291 --> 41:27.458
Calm down.

41:29.708 --> 41:31.333
Who'll tell her?

41:32.458 --> 41:34.375
That's a good question, Doni.

41:41.541 --> 41:44.583
I'll post this one.
We'll take another outside.

41:49.708 --> 41:51.000
Awesome beef, Nando.

41:51.791 --> 41:53.875
It's had a better life than we did.

42:06.333 --> 42:07.208
Hang on.

42:11.083 --> 42:13.250
Hey, brother. All good?

42:13.333 --> 42:15.208
All good, thank the Lord.

42:15.291 --> 42:17.541
-We cool?
-We cool, thank the Lord.

42:18.083 --> 42:19.791
What's up, brother?

42:20.791 --> 42:22.291
I heard you went to Messinho.

42:22.375 --> 42:25.000
That you made a deal. Is that right?

42:25.083 --> 42:27.375
That's right. Gotta keep the business.

42:27.875 --> 42:29.125
Alright, cool.

42:29.208 --> 42:30.166
And my shop?

42:31.208 --> 42:33.625
You forgot your godfather?

42:34.125 --> 42:36.416
No, brother! We're in this together.

42:36.500 --> 42:40.666
If we were, you'd have found
the rat that took our load.

42:42.416 --> 42:43.958
We had another one, right?

42:45.041 --> 42:46.250
Same as before.

42:46.750 --> 42:49.458
If you can't find out
who's ratting us out soon,

42:49.958 --> 42:51.916
you risk losing your own load.

42:53.125 --> 42:54.250
I'm on it, brother.

42:54.333 --> 42:56.708
Brother, do better.

42:56.791 --> 43:00.500
It's time. You're the one in charge.
So make this happen.

43:00.583 --> 43:01.625
You're right.

43:02.291 --> 43:04.458
Don't worry. I won't screw this up.

43:04.958 --> 43:05.916
Got it?

43:06.000 --> 43:08.250
We've got the same appetite. Trust me.

43:08.333 --> 43:09.375
Alright, boy.

43:09.458 --> 43:12.875
You got my respect.
God be with you. Later, man.

43:12.958 --> 43:15.041
Alright, man. Later.

43:20.833 --> 43:22.291
Enjoying the meal?

43:24.708 --> 43:26.250
For two now.

43:27.375 --> 43:28.375
Right.

43:28.875 --> 43:30.000
Don't worry.

43:30.083 --> 43:32.250
I'll help you promote your song.

43:32.333 --> 43:33.958
You guys will help too.

43:34.041 --> 43:35.291
-Yep.
-Yep.

43:35.833 --> 43:37.750
Doni, we're ready for you.

43:38.458 --> 43:40.541
Don't give up. It'll work out.

43:41.041 --> 43:42.291
Doni, one minute.

43:42.791 --> 43:43.625
Let's go.

43:44.125 --> 43:45.583
I'll say your name.

43:46.083 --> 43:47.708
-Alright?
-Cool.

43:48.375 --> 43:49.208
Come on.

44:04.083 --> 44:08.250
Alright, I have the pleasure
of welcoming a very talented MC.

44:08.333 --> 44:11.083
Singing his latest single,

44:11.166 --> 44:13.416
MC Doni!

44:14.083 --> 44:18.208
MC Luzi, our song is on TV!

44:18.291 --> 44:20.750
It's our song! Come on!

44:20.833 --> 44:21.666
It's ours.

44:22.166 --> 44:23.875
Called her over to the house

44:23.958 --> 44:25.458
To go at it no pause

44:25.541 --> 44:27.708
She gon' be working that booty up and down

44:27.791 --> 44:30.375
Just got my tan on, feeling frisky

44:30.458 --> 44:33.000
If we get together, we gon' go kaboom

44:33.083 --> 44:35.416
She likes to scratch, to lick, and to kiss

44:35.500 --> 44:37.833
Her ass is deadly
Leaves me out of breath

44:37.916 --> 44:40.250
I begin to grind ya
I know how to tease ya

44:40.333 --> 44:42.375
I can't hold on anymore

44:42.458 --> 44:43.666
It's too late to stop

44:47.166 --> 44:48.916
She won't stop screaming

44:49.000 --> 44:51.208
Alright, MC Luzi!

44:57.666 --> 44:59.083
Hey, how are you?

44:59.583 --> 45:01.250
Hello, sisters. How are you?

45:02.291 --> 45:03.208
Thanks.

45:03.875 --> 45:07.125
-Where are the prayers?
-We like music too.

45:07.208 --> 45:09.916
-I liked it.
-You did? It's gospel.

45:11.166 --> 45:12.791
Thought you weren't coming.

45:12.875 --> 45:15.958
-You said I'd be your right-hand lady.
-That's better.

45:16.041 --> 45:17.125
Let's get to it.

45:17.208 --> 45:19.666
Please carry these cans over there,

45:19.750 --> 45:20.958
my right-hand lady.

45:22.750 --> 45:25.541
Boys, can you get the things
from the truck?

45:25.625 --> 45:26.875
-Sure.
-Thanks.

45:27.458 --> 45:29.208
Rita, this is heavy!

45:29.708 --> 45:31.666
I won't need to go to the gym.

45:33.125 --> 45:35.000
How do you think I work out?

45:35.083 --> 45:36.208
I can see that.

45:38.000 --> 45:40.708
When were you gonna tell me
about that stud?

45:43.458 --> 45:45.083
Awesome car, honey.

45:46.000 --> 45:47.791
-Here, buddy.
-Thank you.

45:50.083 --> 45:51.416
-Did you like it?
-Yep.

45:52.041 --> 45:53.666
-You drive.
-Why?

45:54.416 --> 45:57.000
-It's yours now.
-Nando, are you serious?

45:57.083 --> 45:59.458
-I'm serious.
-Really, love? For real?

46:00.708 --> 46:02.291
It's so me.

46:02.875 --> 46:05.083
It's so fancy!

46:05.166 --> 46:06.666
Check this out!

46:07.833 --> 46:10.416
-Isn't it me?
-Get used to it.

46:10.500 --> 46:11.583
Get in, honey.

46:15.333 --> 46:17.041
It's so smooth!

46:18.458 --> 46:20.666
I love this new car smell.

46:23.958 --> 46:26.125
You know I'm here for you, right?

46:31.166 --> 46:33.708
If you need anything, count on me.

46:33.791 --> 46:35.333
Now with a brand-new car.

46:36.166 --> 46:37.583
She's so badass.

46:38.916 --> 46:41.750
-Awesome performance, man.
-Amazing, bro.

46:41.833 --> 46:43.541
People were screaming!

46:43.625 --> 46:44.541
Check this out.

46:46.041 --> 46:47.333
You did it, Doni!

46:47.875 --> 46:49.708
Nice to meet you. Theo Ribeiro.

46:49.791 --> 46:50.625
-Hey.
-Cool?

46:50.708 --> 46:51.750
Great music, man.

46:51.833 --> 46:53.791
-Let's do a collab.
-Deal.

46:53.875 --> 46:55.500
Give me a call. Bye, guys.

46:55.583 --> 46:56.750
-Cool.
-Later, Theo.

46:58.666 --> 47:02.041
Man, the guy was all over you.

47:02.666 --> 47:04.833
He nearly kissed your ass.

47:07.500 --> 47:09.333
Yo, dude, your performance is trending.

47:09.416 --> 47:11.000
You broke the Internet.

47:11.666 --> 47:14.083
It's blowing up.

47:14.166 --> 47:15.250
Where's Luzi?

47:15.750 --> 47:18.041
Talking to her manager outside.

47:22.916 --> 47:24.416
Fucking idiot.

47:25.625 --> 47:28.125
No. Not you, we're cool.

47:28.625 --> 47:30.041
It's these people.

47:30.125 --> 47:32.125
We're just a cog in the wheel.

47:32.208 --> 47:35.250
These managers only see dollar signs.

47:35.333 --> 47:37.000
They play with our dreams.

47:37.583 --> 47:39.708
So many talented people in the hood.

47:39.791 --> 47:42.583
And these leeches screw us over.

47:43.791 --> 47:44.875
It's fucked up.

47:50.583 --> 47:54.666
But believe in yourself.
You've got talent. Believe in your dream.

47:54.750 --> 47:57.666
-I know, but…
-Hang on.

47:58.833 --> 47:59.833
Hello?

47:59.916 --> 48:02.833
It was amazing, honey! Congratulations!

48:03.333 --> 48:04.541
Glad you liked it.

48:04.625 --> 48:05.583
I loved it!

48:05.666 --> 48:10.041
I'll make that steak you love
to celebrate.

48:10.125 --> 48:12.833
Alright, make plenty.
I'm bringing some friends over.

48:18.458 --> 48:19.458
Okay.

48:20.250 --> 48:23.291
I have to go now. I'll see you later.

48:23.916 --> 48:25.041
Everything okay?

48:25.875 --> 48:27.833
I've got customers. Bye, Son.

48:27.916 --> 48:31.833
Hello. I've come
for my bread rolls, Lucrécia.

52:24.375 --> 52:28.125
Subtitle translation by: Jonathan Williams
